n14-expedition-warning-5min = WARNING: 5 minutes remaining! Head to the return point to exit safely.
n14-expedition-warning-1min = WARNING: 1 minute remaining! Return to the exit point immediately!
n14-expedition-warning-30sec = FINAL WARNING: 30 seconds! You will be forcibly extracted!

n14-expedition-extracting = Time's up! Extracting all personnel...
